<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-2910] libevent is not really optional</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-2910</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;According to &lt;a href=&quot;http://thrift.apache.org/docs/install/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;the docs&lt;/a&gt;, libevent is optional, which is actually not really the case. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;./configure --without-libevent
make
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;leads to&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;make[4]: Entering directory &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;/home/jens/Arbeitsfl&#228;che/Thrift/lib/cpp/test&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
make[4]: *** No rule to make target &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;../../../lib/cpp/libthriftnb.la&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, needed by &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;processor_test&apos;&lt;/span&gt;. 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
